      "content": "yo u ever notice how the autocomplete on search engines has been acting super weird lately?? like i was typing stuff about my neighborhood and it kept suggesting phrases that had nothing to do with what i was looking for, almost like it was trying to tell me something or reacting to me specifically. it feels way too deliberate to be a glitch.",
