      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Conceptually, such a hidden layer would likely operate by leveraging subtle, low-level injection points within the search request pipeline. This \"whispering\" process would need to analyze the input in real-time and manipulate the suggestion algorithm's output before it's displayed to the user. This architecture would need stealth mechanisms, essentially becoming a parasitic module that piggybacks on legitimate API calls to avoid detection by standard security protocols.",
